    <entry>
      <title>Hello New World</title>
      <link href="/p/4a17b156.html"/>
      <url>/p/4a17b156.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>&emsp;&emsp;吧博客迁移到了Volantis上，很多标签插件用法发生了变化。于是修改这篇文章，以便自己翻阅。</p><span id="more"></span><h2 id="文字"><a href="#文字" class="headerlink" title="文字"></a>文字</h2><h3 id="·-字体"><a href="#·-字体" class="headerlink" title="· 字体"></a>· 字体</h3><div class="tabs" id="tab-1"><ul class="nav-tabs"><li class="tab active"><a class="#tab-1-1">效果</a></li><li class="tab"><a class="#tab-1-2">写法</a></li></ul><div class="tab-content"><div class="tab-pane active" id="tab-1-1"><p class='p red'>可以改字体的颜色</p><p class='p large'>还可以改字体的大小</p><p class='p logo huge center'>还可以居中使用</p><p class='p logo huge center'>超大毛泽东字体</p>重要的是可以在各级标题中使用</div><div class="tab-pane" id="tab-1-2"><figure class="highlight mkd"><figcaption><span>字体</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% p 参数1,参数2,参数3...,文字内容 %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th><strong>属性</strong></th><th><strong>可选值</strong></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>字体</td><td>logo, code</td></tr><tr><td>颜色</td><td>red, yellow, green, cyan, blue, gray</td></tr><tr><td>大小</td><td>small, h4, h3, h2, h1, large, huge, ultra</td></tr><tr><td>对齐方向</td><td>left, center, right</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></div><h3 id="·-文字样式"><a href="#·-文字样式" class="headerlink" title="· 文字样式"></a>· 文字样式</h3><div class="tabs" id="tab-1"><ul class="nav-tabs"><li class="tab active"><a class="#tab-1-1">效果</a></li><li class="tab"><a class="#tab-1-2">写法</a></li></ul><div class="tab-content"><div class="tab-pane active" id="tab-1-1"><p><u>下划线</u>  <emp>加重号</emp>  <wavy>波浪线</wavy><br><kbd>alt</kbd> + <kbd>f4</kbd>  <psw>黑暗</psw>剑</p></div><div class="tab-pane" id="tab-1-2"><figure class="highlight mkd"><figcaption><span>文字样式</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% u 下划线 %&#125;  &#123;% emp 加重号 %&#125;  &#123;% wavy 波浪线 %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% kbd 按键图标 %&#125;  &#123;% psw 数据删除 %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></div></div><h3 id="·-代码块"><a href="#·-代码块" class="headerlink" title="· 代码块"></a>· 代码块</h3><figure class="highlight cs"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="built_in">string</span> type = <span class="string">&quot;Code-Block&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">main</span>(<span class="params"></span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    print(type);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>code：<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># ```语言类型</span><br><span class="line"># 代码块</span><br><span class="line"># ```</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><hr><h2 id="·-引言"><a href="#·-引言" class="headerlink" title="· 引言"></a>· 引言</h2><p>我没说过这句话。<br>&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;——鲁迅</p><ul><li>code：<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># &#123;% cq %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"># 内容</span><br><span class="line"># &#123;% endcq %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><hr><h2 id="·-Note"><a href="#·-Note" class="headerlink" title="· Note"></a>· Note</h2><ul><li>code:<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note Note类型 %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">内容</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>或<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;note Note类型&quot;</span>&gt;</span>内容<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><hr><h2 id="·-图标"><a href="#·-图标" class="headerlink" title="· 图标"></a>· 图标</h2><p>&emsp;&emsp;<i class="fa fa-steam-square"></i> <i class="fa fa-pencil"></i> <i class="fa fa-gamepad"></i> <i class="fa fa-battery-three-quarters"></i></p><ul><li>code：<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">i</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;fa FontAwesome图标名&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">i</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><hr><h2 id="·-Emoji"><a href="#·-Emoji" class="headerlink" title="· Emoji"></a>· Emoji</h2><p>&emsp;&emsp;🌶️💩💉💧🐂🍺<br>&emsp;&emsp;插件里的不完整，直接去<a href="https://emojipedia.org/" title="emojipedia">EmojiPedia</a>搜索复制会更方便。</p><hr><h1 id="图表"><a href="#图表" class="headerlink" title="图表"></a>图表</h1><h2 id="·-图片"><a href="#·-图片" class="headerlink" title="· 图片"></a>· 图片</h2><center><div style="width:200px;display:inline-block"><p style="font-size:5px;text-align:center"><img src="/images/image.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/images/image.png" srcset="data:image/p